"Requirements"
-Install the "Arduino IDE"
It is an IDE for working with devices like Arduino and NodeMCU, you can upload the code to your device from here.
-Install Libraries
"NodeMCU"
<ESP8266WiFi.h>
<BlynkSimpleEsp8266.h>
"Arduino UNO"
<Keypad.h>
<Wire.h>
<LiquidCrystal_I2C.h>
<Servo.h>
<SoftwareSerial.h>
